OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FThe sister of a woman murdered by her
OL,7,Fboyfriend in Sunderland has urged
OL,8,Fanyone suffering with domestic
OL,9,Fviolence to speak out before it is too
OL,10,Flate.
OL,12,FMelissa Eastick was murdered by her
OL,13,Fpartner Stephen Todd - who was already
OL,14,Fserving a suspended sentence for
OL,15,Fattacking her.
