OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FThe 36-year-old mother was described
OL,7,Fin court as "tiny" and vulnerable -
OL,8,Fand those in court heard how she was
OL,9,Fleft with over 100 injuries from Todd,
OL,10,Fwho was handed a life sentence with a
OL,11,Fminimum of 21 years before he is
OL,12,Feligible for parole.
OL,14,FSam Turnbull, Melissa's sister, told
OL,15,FITV Tyne Tees that she wants anyone
OL,16,Fsuffering with domestic violence to
OL,17,F"speak out and seek help - before it's
OL,18,Ftoo late for them".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
