OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FAs part of Todd's suspended sentence
OL,7,Ffor attacking Melissa, he was ordered
OL,8,Fto complete a 'building better
OL,9,Frelationships' course.
OL,11,FHe attended part of this course while
OL,12,FMelissa lay dying in his home at the
OL,13,Fhands of his abuse.
OL,15,FMs Turnbull told how the first time
OL,16,Fthe family heard Todd had attended the
OL,17,Fcourse as Melissa was dying was in
OL,18,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
