OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FShe said the course had "not worked"
OL,7,Fand that for some who attend the
OL,8,Fcourses it "just goes over their
OL,9,Fheads."
OL,11,F"I have heard he has done this
OL,12,Fprevious partners, Melissa isn't the
OL,13,Ffirst," Ms Turnbull said. "I don't
OL,14,Fthink he should have been released the
OL,15,Ffirst time around."
OL,17,FThe extent of Melissa's injuries have
OL,18,Fdeeply upset her family.
