OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FShe said the court process had been
OL,7,F"long and draining" as the family
OL,8,Fsearched for answers.
OL,10,F"He had no remorse, he wasn't
OL,11,Fbothered. He looked over a couple of
OL,12,Ftimes at us in court.
OL,14,F"He's disgusting, absolutely
OL,15,Fdisgusting," she said.
OL,17,FTodd, 41, of Buttermere Street,
OL,18,FSunderland, pleaded guilty to murder
OL,19,Fon the basis there was no intention to
OL,20,Fkill.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
