OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,FHe has nine previous conviction and
OL,7,Ffour cautions - but just one of those
OL,8,Fis in relation to Melissa.
OL,10,FMrs Justice Lambert sentenced him to
OL,11,Flife behind bars on Wednesday 6
OL,12,FNovember.
OL,14,FThe judge said Todd inflicted mental
OL,15,Fand physical suffering on Melissa
OL,16,Fbefore her death and added: "For the
OL,17,Flast 24 hours of her life, at least,
OL,18,Fshe was profoundly unconscious because
OL,19,Fof the brain injury, but medical
OL,20,Fevidence as a whole shows your
OL,21,Fviolence was repeated and brutal.
