OL,3,C'Speak out before it's too late,' say
OL,4,Cfamily of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,6,F"You accept you battered her
OL,7,Frepeatedly. She was a petite and
OL,8,Ffragile woman and would have been in
OL,9,Fno physical condition to protect
OL,10,Fherself.
OL,12,F"It must have been a terrifying and
OL,13,Fimmensely painful experience for
OL,14,FMelissa."
